{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/object-oriented-programming/create-a-method-on-an-object","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"object-oriented-programming","demoType":null,"title":"Napravi put na nečemu","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Stvari mogu imati poseban tip karakteristika, nazvan <dfn>njia</dfn>.</p>\n<p>Metoda je svojstvo koje je funkcionalno. Ovo dodaje različito ponašanje objektu. Evo primera za <code>duck</code> sa metodama:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">let duck = {\n  name: \"Aflac\",\n  numLegs: 2,\n  sayName: function() {return \"The name of this duck is \" + duck.name + \".\";}\n};\nduck.sayName();\n</code></pre>\n<p>Ovaj primer dodaje metodu <code>sayName</code>, koja vraća rečenicu sa imenom objekta <code>duck</code>. Obrati pažnju da metoda koristi <code>duck.name</code> u naredbi <code>return</code>. Sledeći izazov će pokazati još jedan način da se to uradi.</p>\n</section>","id":"587d7dad367417b2b2512b75","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Ako zavisiš od <code>dog</code>, daj put koji se zove <code>sayLegs</code>. Taj put bi trebalo da vrati rečenicu <code>This dog has 4 legs.</code></p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301318,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/object-oriented-programming/create-a-method-on-an-object"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"let dog = {\n  name: \"Spot\",\n  numLegs: 4,\n\n};\n\ndog.sayLegs();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>dog.sayLegs()</code> Trebalo bi da bude funkcija.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof dog.sayLegs === 'function');"},{"text":"<p><code>dog.sayLegs()</code> Trebalo bi da vrati sekvencu karaktera koja je data – zapamtite da su interpunkcijski znaci i razmaci važni.</p>","testString":"assert(dog.sayLegs() === 'This dog has 4 legs.');"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/#object-oriented-programming","dashedName":"create-a-method-on-an-object","certification":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"object-oriented-programming","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/object-oriented-programming/make-code-more-reusable-with-the-this-keyword","prevChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/object-oriented-programming/use-dot-notation-to-access-the-properties-of-an-object","id":"587d7dad367417b2b2512b75","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"const funModule = (function () {\n  return {\n    isCuteMixin: obj => {\n      obj.isCute = () => true;\n    },\n    singMixin: obj => {\n      obj.sing = () => console.log(\"Singing to an awesome tune\");\n    }\n  };\n})();","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/object-oriented-programming/create-a-method-on-an-object"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}